"signal_description": "The SIGNAL query is calculating the percentage of certain events in relation to the creation of Purchase Order (PO) items. Specifically, it is counting the number of cases in the 'defaultview-57' table where the 'event_name' column matches either 'Update PO Item Material', 'Update PO Item Quantity', 'Update PO Item Net Price', 'Update PO Item Plant', or 'Update PO Confirmed Delivery Date'. This count is then divided by the total number of cases where the 'event_name' column matches 'Create PO Item'. The result is multiplied by 100 to convert it into a percentage. Therefore, this query provides the percentage of these specific update events out of all the events related to the creation of PO items."
